{"tid":567472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓冬奧再現黑哨，直接判韓選手入決賽","createTime":"2018-02-21T01:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T06:48:22.000Z","uid":25345,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b752919ab753ce32a13ab156f664d8391dd2bf","tid":567472,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T01:32:45.000Z","msg":"平昌冬奧再爆疑似「黑哨」事件，上周六短道速滑女子1,500米準決賽，22歲南韓美女選手金雅朗疑似推跌加拿大的聖格萊斯，令其滑出賽道，但裁判卻判罰聖格萊斯犯規，使金雅朗入決賽。雖然她在決賽只獲第四，但已遭內地傳媒大肆抨擊。（無綫財經資訊台今日6:00pm直播）<br />\n<br />\n當時聖格萊斯欲在內檔趕過金雅朗，後者疑似伸左手推向聖格萊斯，令其倒地並滑出賽道，賽會最後判聖格萊斯犯規，金雅朗則排小組預賽第一入決賽，雖在決賽只獲第四，但她的隊友崔敏靜奪金，中國選手李靳宇獲銀。內地傳媒炮轟平昌冬奧「主場雞」，稱南韓速滑隊早有前科；又指中國隊的韓天宇，在1,000米賽事無辜被指犯規遭取消資格等。<br />\n而南韓女隊在速滑團體追逐賽出局後，選手金寶凜疑賽後埋怨隊友，昨遭南韓網民在其社交網絡「洗版」。<br />\n同日冰舞項目，周一因戰衣鬆脫而露點的法國女將柏芭達姬絲，與隊友施沙朗昨出戰賽事第二部份自由舞，得到123.35高分，但仍不敵加拿大組合迪莎維杜與史葛摩亞奪銀<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180221/small/s1100.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180221%2Fsmall%2Fs1100.jpg&h=c38dbcec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b7dbb31352ac1e8f05aa928a5b0d92e2d0cbd0b","tid":567472,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"''但已遭內地傳媒大肆抨擊。（無綫財經資訊台今日6:00pm直播）''<br />\n<br />\n即係由負公信力既CCTVB 寫架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529e679aa23977e23e71459bd7119ba21637698c","tid":567472,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0b7dbb31352ac1e8f05aa928a5b0d92e2d0cbd0b","tid":567472,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"''但已遭內地傳媒大肆抨擊。（無綫財經資訊台今日6:00pm直播）''<br />\n<br />\n即係由負公信力既CCTVB 寫架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T01:51:02.000Z","msg":"成編野係咁寫人地黑哨你大陸人"},{"pid":"26fe20bc168669ff69f3f7965b474ca31005d99a","tid":567472,"uid":2640,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T01:52:27.000Z","msg":"周一因戰衣鬆脫而露點的法國女將柏芭達姬絲<br />\n<br />\n因航咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw 有無圖"},{"pid":"e002593341b3cfba01507aaab0cccd937184f146","tid":567472,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26fe20bc168669ff69f3f7965b474ca31005d99a","tid":567472,"uid":2640,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T01:52:27.000Z","msg":"周一因戰衣鬆脫而露點的法國女將柏芭達姬絲<br />\n<br />\n因航咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw 有無圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T01:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a6c49f379d22b9e2715cdc8661bbaafc8a1bb0","tid":567472,"uid":83950,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:01:19.000Z","msg":"泡菜佬黑哨都唔係第一日啦 仲記唔記得02年<br />\n全撚部泡菜冇個無辜"},{"pid":"b074286b0e7d4876a053de979adf6d1797dd5936","tid":567472,"uid":38540,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:03:17.000Z","msg":"賤種泡狗玩咩都要作下弊"},{"pid":"93b49089deec932786a9bdf375ecd68f221f5c15","tid":567472,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:03:49.000Z","msg":"泡菜最撚黑架啦體育方面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3cb30777304a81475947cbb0c6b9dc0ac6ad941","tid":567472,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:05:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4830c2404f96d98f09c05b1d3b9e3d3eda1f5d17","tid":567472,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/sports/page/800/2015/07/11/phpPrYpBe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fsports%2Fpage%2F800%2F2015%2F07%2F11%2FphpPrYpBe.jpg&h=67bc3f59&s={SIZE}\" 